{"tid":1956744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【光復區會】去年區選年輕人投票率創新高達73% 首次超越長者","createTime":"2020-04-03T11:31:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T17:27:05.000Z","uid":5812,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"a881fde3a3b06a0637fc6f5b1c8e0205cbe51c35","tid":1956744,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T11:31:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XJUPgMp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXJUPgMp.png&h=d7730411&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n選舉事務處今日回覆不同年齡分層於2019年區議會選舉中的投票率，年輕選民投票率終於首次高於長者投票率。18至35歲的年輕人投票率達73%，創出歷史新高，66歲或以上的長者投票率則只有65.3%，兩者相距約8個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n回歸以來的區議會選舉、立法會選舉，長者投票率一直均較年輕選民為高，這個情況持續逾20年從沒打破。但去年區議會選舉，在反修例運動的情緒下，這個投票情況終於改變，年輕人投票率首次高於長者。按照選舉事務處的回覆，去年區選中，年輕人（18至35歲）投票率為73.1%，中年人（36至65歲）為72.8%，長者（66歲以上）為65.3%，年輕人的投票率高於長者7.8個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n以往長者的投票率均高於整體投票率，不過今屆例外，今屆整體投票率為71%，但長者投票率只有65.3%。相反，以往年輕人的投票率均低於整體投票率一大截，但今屆卻例外，年輕人的投票率高於整體投票率約2個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200403/WEP53UDHKK36G3MD4S5RIRAMMY/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200403%2FWEP53UDHKK36G3MD4S5RIRAMMY%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2BjBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=dccf760a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200403%2FWEP53UDHKK36G3MD4S5RIRAMMY%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=08e1569f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200403/WEP53UDHKK36G3MD4S5RIRAMMY/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"6